The following macros are defined for the 'lpc' command:

macro-               meaning-
ENV(x)               environment(x)
TP                   this_player()
FP                   find_player()
FL                   find_living()
PR(x,y)              present(x, y)
FO(x)                find_object(x)
TEOB(ob, mesg)       tell_object(ob, mesg);

If you know of any other useful macros, feel free to mail blue.
